oximate even to error $1/2 -\n2^{-m}$. Our construction achieves the same amplification in the work of Thaler\n(ICALP, 2016), by composing a function with $O(\\log n)$ {\\em deterministic\nquery complexity}.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 13 Jun 2016 16:13:28 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 14 Oct 2016 16:58:33 GMT"}],"update_date":"2016-10-17"}
