e KBHsSH. It is plausible, therefore, that\nsufficiently precise Very Long Baseline Interferometric observations of BH\ncandidates can constrain this model.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 14 Jun 2016 08:33:08 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 19 Oct 2016 12:21:43 GMT"}],"update_date":"2016-11-02"}
