icles are surprisingly pushed away, suggesting that\nsuch \"boosted geometries\" are ruled by a sort of \"antigravity effect\".\nEventually, the equivalence with the coordinate shift method is invoked in\norder to demonstrate that all $\\delta^2$ terms appearing in the Riemann\ncurvature tensor give vanishing contribution in distributional sense.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 14 Jun 2016 08:59:31 GMT"}],"update_date":"2016-06-15"}
