ussed can also capture\nthe increase of the relative fluctuation amplitude observed in the far SOL. It\nis also shown that several scenarios are compatible with the broadening of the\nSOL, which could be caused by charge exchange interactions with neutral\nparticles or by a significant radial acceleration of the filaments.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 14 Jun 2016 09:08:40 GMT"}],"update_date":"2016-11-24"}
