ities. In some cases we show\nthat the Peres-Horodecki criterion is both sufficient and necessary.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 14 Jun 2016 10:55:46 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 28 Jun 2016 11:02:01 GMT"}],"update_date":"2016-06-29"}
