 at most 3 these problems can be solved in polynomial time (even in\nlogspace), while starting from color class size 4 they become W[P]-hard.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 14 Jun 2016 14:19:09 GMT"}],"update_date":"2016-06-15"}
